    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Makefile发现算法的时序图，核心流程是CLI调用Discovery Service去扫描项目里的Makefile，然后解析目标。这里涉及到FinTech相关的几个服务模块，比如LedgerService和FraudDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CLI",
        "Discovery Service",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那Discovery Service具体怎么发现Makefile呢？是直接遍历File System还是有特殊机制？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery Service",
        "File System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有个trick：Discovery Service会先创建一个临时的Makefile，里面定义一个_list_makefiles目标，然后通过make命令本身来输出所有被include的Makefile列表。所以第一步是DS向FS创建临时文件，拿到temp path。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery Service",
        "File System",
        "make command",
        "temp file",
        "_list_makefiles"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以第一步用FinTech_AuthVault色块包裹，标注\"Create temp Makefile\"。然后第二步DS调用make命令执行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "Discovery Service",
        "make command"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，第二步用FinTech_PaymentGateway色块。DS执行make -f temp -f Makefile _list_makefiles，Make返回MAKEFILE_LIST输出，然后DS要清理掉那个temp file。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Discovery Service",
        "make command",
        "MAKEFILE_LIST",
        "temp file"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加第二步。那第三步就是解析输出？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery Service"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第三步用FinTech_TransactionQueue色块，DS自己解析：过滤掉temp file路径，把相对路径resolve成absolute path，最后返回给CLI一个字符串数组。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "Discovery Service",
        "CLI",
        "file paths"
